The Benelli SuperSport Semi-Auto Shotgun has highly advanced features needed to win sporting clays competitions. A QuadraFit™ modular buttstock allows shooters to easily adjust the drop, cast, comb height, and length of pull in minutes. A lightweight ventilated, stepped rib, with a red bar front sight and mid bead, provide an excellent sighting plane. title: For Sale:  FEG PJK-9HP Hi Power Clone-great condition
postcontent:
Looking to sell my FEG PJK-9HP 9mm semi- auto pistol. The FEG was made in Budapest, Hungary. This is an all steel pistol and is a true clone of the Browning Hi-Power as 95%+ of the parts are interchangeable. I have a Browning and they are mirror images of each other. Great book on Amazon, Decoding the FEG Hi Power, will tell you a lot about these pistols. Imported by KBI. I understand the PJK are the initials of the owner of KBI. FEG filed for bankruptcy in 2005 so these guns are getting harder to find. Comes with three 12 round magazines and one 20 round magazine (very rare). Very clean with no loss of the nice bluing or holster wear. Shoots great but just trying to thin my FEG pistols to fund another project.
I also have an FEG GKK-45 here on Arms List and will make a deal for both!!!
Must have current CPL and be willing to meet at my local police station.
Please see the pictures and please contact me via email with offers/questions/more pictures.
